Subject: Engine smoothness.

The Suby engines must be an order of magnitude smoother than any of the VW 
engines I've had. Some of my engines have been smoother than others. All had 
their internal components balanced. Anyone know what might account for 
smoothness differences? My current engine is a bit of a shaker even with a 
counter-balanced crank, a first for me. Its a bit disappointing.

